        "jsCode": "// Unwrap leads array into individual items for SplitInBatches\nconst leads = $input.first().json;\nif(!Array.isArray(leads)||leads.length===0) return [{json:{done:true,message:'No NEW leads'}}];\nreturn leads.map(l=>({json:l}));"
