    "setup": "Before importing, set these n8n Variables (Settings > Variables): SUPABASE_URL, SUPABASE_ANON_KEY, SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY, GROQ_API_KEY, SHEET_ID (the ID from your Google Sheet URL between /d/ and /edit).",
